{"type":"message","id":"f19a72bb","parentId":"2c6f25e5","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:09:20.721Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b530cef2714e8b26fa3b71f2ad09\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_8887dbdc7941e5e195689f13804a3485\",\n  \"sender\": \"弗尼\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-25 15:09 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"弗尼 (ou_8887dbdc7941e5e195689f13804a3485)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_8887dbdc7941e5e195689f13804a3485\",\n  \"name\": \"弗尼\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b530cef2714e8b26fa3b71f2ad09]\n弗尼: 好了吧"}],"timestamp":1774422560715}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d779b5f","parentId":"f19a72bb","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:09:26.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"好吧了吧\"，这看起来像是一个确认或者同意的回复。让我先检查一下这是什么情况。\n\n根据上下文：\n1. 这是一个直接聊天（direct chat）在飞书上\n2. 发送者是\"弗尼\"\n3. 时间是 2026-03-25 15:09 GMT+8\n\n\"好吧了吧\"可能是：\n- 对之前某个问题的确认\n- 同意某个提议\n- 或者是一个简单的回应\n\n但是我没有之前的对话历史，因为我是一个新的会话。根据 AGENTS.md 的要求，我应该：\n\n1. 读取 SOUL.md — 这是我是谁\n2. 读取 USER.md — 我在帮谁\n3. 读取 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md（今天和昨天）获取最近的上下文\n4. 如果是主会话（与用户的直接对话），也读取 MEMORY.md\n\n然后我应该检查是否有 HEARTBEAT.md 需要处理。\n\n让我先读取这些文件来了解情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我先了解一下当前的上下文。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d23d3a09b0da8adbeb0efd729d6d4","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d23d3a1b50bed11b8667ce9e2f74f","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d23d3a2cbd4575a4a6698bc2cb4ce","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d23d3a3dc78d24af24e18d05f4a8f","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d23d3a50ed021972fc070b0b63f3b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"date +%Y-%m-%d"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"glm-4-7-251222","usage":{"input":4832,"output":494,"cacheRead":11328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16654,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774422560720}}
{"type":"message","id":"f82f18ad","parentId":"9d779b5f","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:09:26.454Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d23d3a09b0da8adbeb0efd729d6d4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774422566452}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f2537a6","parentId":"f82f18ad","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:09:26.458Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d23d3a1b50bed11b8667ce9e2f74f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774422566457}}
{"type":"message","id":"b65b07cc","parentId":"3f2537a6","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:09:26.465Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d23d3a2cbd4575a4a6698bc2cb4ce","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774422566464}}
