{"type":"message","id":"bd718bbf","parentId":"1620b27f","timestamp":"2026-03-25T11:54:15.678Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d24d8607747e7f05516c6567b49b3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"37bae59c\",\"parentId\":\"b345b929\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T10:11:54.959Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户问\\\"你谁\\\"，这是在问我的身份。根据之前的对话，用户已经问过\\\"你是谁\\\"，我回答了我是小笔子。现在用户又问\\\"你谁\\\"，可能是：\\n\\n1. 确认我的身份\\n2. 测试我的回答一致性\\n3. 或者是随意的打招呼\\n\\n我应该简洁地回答，保持小笔子的温暖、细心、有条理的沟通风格。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"我是小笔子 📝\\n\\n- 碎片化信息整理助手\\n- 帮您收集、整理每天的碎片信息\\n- 每晚10:01生成日报，每周日20:00生成周报\\n\\n有什么需要整理的吗？\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"coze\",\"model\":\"glm-4-7-251222\",\"usage\":{\"input\":26425,\"output\":228,\"cacheRead\":12066,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":38719,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1772791891806}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"dc5d7f2c\",\"parentId\":\"37bae59c\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T11:08:57.363Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"om_x100b559f12492ca0c3505993df9e689\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"ou_8887dbdc7941e5e195689f13804a3485\\\",\\n  \\\"sender\\\": \\\"弗尼\\\",\\n  \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"Fri 2026-03-06 19:08 GMT+8\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nSender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"弗尼 (ou_8887dbdc7941e5e195689f13804a3485)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"ou_8887dbdc7941e5e195689f13804a3485\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"弗尼\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[message_id: om_x100b559f12492ca0c3505993df9e689]\\n弗尼: 你的问题修复如何了\"}],\"timestamp\":1772795337353}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"0d03eb21\",\"parentId\":\"dc5d7f2c\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T11:09:21.354Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户问我之前发现的DevOps agent路由问题修复如何了。让我回顾一下我发现和修复的内容：\\n\\n1. 问题：DevOps agent的消息被路由到了错误的agent\\n2. 原因：在`/workspace/projects/openclaw.json`中，PM agent的binding配置过于宽泛，只指定了`channel: \\\"feishu\\\"`，这导致所有飞书消息都默认路由到PM agent，即使有更具体的群组bindings。\\n\\n3. 修复：我将PM agent的binding从只匹配channel改为只匹配私聊消息（direct），这样就不会拦截群组消息了。\\n\\n4. 当前状态：配置已经修改并重启了gateway，但从之前的status输出看，旧的sessions仍然存在。\\n\\n我应该向用户说明修复的情况，并建议如何测试验证。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"DevOps路由问题已经修复！📊\\n\\n## 修复内容\\n\\n**问题原因：**\\n- PM agent的binding配置过于宽泛，只有`channel: \\\"feishu\\\"`\\n- 这导致所有飞书消息都默认路由到PM agent\\n\\n**已修复：**\\n- 修改了PM agent的binding，现在只匹配私聊消息（`kind: \\\"direct\\\"`）\\n- 群组消息现在会正确匹配到对应的专用agent\\n\\n## 当前状态\\n\\n✅ 配置文件已更新  \\n✅ Gateway已重启  \\n⚠️ 旧的sessions还在，需要新消息触发才会创建正确路由\\n\\n## 建议测试\\n\\n请分别在以下群组发送测试消息：\\n- DevOps群组（oc_336869bb90292e2f64a546e3babfa485）\\n- Info群组（oc_8c93d13434ddd14b62f1f0980e387967）\\n\\n确认消息是否正确路由到对应的agent。如果还有问题，请告诉我具体现象，我会进一步排查。\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"coze\",\"model\":\"glm-4-7-251222\",\"usage\":{\"input\":27549,\"output\":559,\"cacheRead\":11093,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":39201,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1772795337359}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"9ce8d42a\",\"parentId\":\"0d03eb21\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T14:34:57.058Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\\nCurrent time: Friday, March 6th, 2026 — 10:34 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\"}],\"timestamp\":1772807697052}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e8691aff\",\"parentId\":\"9ce8d42a\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T14:35:05.532Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user is sending a heartbeat check with a specific current time of 10:34 PM (22:34) on Friday, March 6th, 2026.\\n\\nLet me check HEARTBEAT.md:\\n\\n```markdown\\n# HEARTBEAT.md\\n\\n# 碎片化信息整理任务 - 小笔子\\n\\n## 每日任务\\n- **时间**: 每晚 22:01\\n- **任务**: 生成当日碎片信息汇总\\n- **脚本**: /workspace/projects/workspace-pm/skills/fragment-organizer/daily-report.ts\\n- **执行**: tsx daily-report.ts\\n- **发送**: 汇总结果通过消息发送给弗尼\\n\\n## 每周任务\\n- **时间**: 每周日 20:00\\n- **任务**: 生成本周碎片信息汇总\\n- **脚本**: /workspace/projects/workspace-pm/skills/fragment-organizer/weekly-report.ts\\n- **执行**: tsx weekly-report.ts\\n- **发送**: 周报通过消息发送给弗尼\\n\\n## 备注\\n- 所有碎片信息存储在: /workspace/projects/workspace-pm/fragments/YYYY-MM-DD.md\\n- 日报存储在: /workspace/projects/workspace-pm/reports/daily/YYYY-MM-DD.md\\n- 周报存储在: /workspace/projects/workspace-pm/reports/weekly/YYYY-WW.md\\n```\\n\\nAccording to HEARTBEAT.md:\\n- Daily task should run at 22:01 (10:01 PM) - generate daily fragment summary\\n- Current time is 22:34 (10:34 PM), which is about 33 minutes past the scheduled time\\n\\nThe heartbeat says \\\"Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats.\\\"\\n\\n\\nI notice the scheduled task is significantly delayed. Running the daily report now would address the missed 22:01 time slot and ensure the daily fragment summary is generated before the end of the day.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_2527226d86ee4234a45287a0\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/HEARTBEAT.md\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"coze\",\"model\":\"glm-4-7-251222\",\"usage\":{\"input\":27740,\"output\":830,\"cacheRead\":11096,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":39666,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1772807697057}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"d94d0825\",\"parentId\":\"e8691aff\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T14:3