不同的信息给你，你存下后回复我\\\"收到🫡\\\"即可，然后每晚10:01整理全天我给你的碎片信息汇总给我，每周日晚上8点整理这周我给你的碎片化信息，你需要在workspace存储所有我粘贴给你的信息，方便我调阅\\nnpm warn exec The following package was not found and will be installed: tsx@4.21.0\\n\\nProcess exited with code 0.\"}],\"details\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"sessionId\":\"glow-river\",\"exitCode\":0,\"aggregated\":\"npm warn exec The following package was not found and will be installed: tsx@4.21.0\\n# 📅 每日碎片信息汇总\\n\\n## 2026-03-06 - 22:35\\n\\n**共收集 2 条碎片信息**\\n\\n---\\n\\n# 碎片化信息 - 2026-03-06\\n\\n## [16:25:00]\\n弗尼: 你是小笔子，专门帮我整理碎片化信息，我会每天粘贴不同的信息给你，你存下后回复我\\\"收到🫡\\\"即可，然后每晚10:01整理全天我给你的碎片信息汇总给我，每周日晚上8点整理这周我给你的碎片化信息，你需要在workspace存储所有我粘贴给你的信息，方便我调阅\\n\\n\\n\",\"name\":\"cd /workspace/projects/wo...lls/fragment-organizer\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1772807729872}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e081b6be\",\"parentId\":\"015b7a45\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T14:35:32.547Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Good! The daily report script ran successfully and collected 2 fragments from today (2026-03-06). However, I notice the output only shows fragments from the conversation history, but it doesn't show the actual daily report being sent to 弗尼. \\n\\nLet me check if there's a mechanism to send this report to 弗尼. The HEARTBEAT.md says \\\"发送: 汇总结果通过消息发送给弗尼\\\" but the script output doesn't show that it was sent.\\n\\nLet me check the daily-report.ts to see if it has the messaging functionality.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_b9ecab84ba464a6ba1ea7203\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/skills/fragment-organizer/daily-report.ts\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"coze\",\"model\":\"glm-4-7-251222\",\"usage\":{\"input\":175,\"output\":268,\"cacheRead\":39950,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":40393,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1772807729876}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"80775600\",\"parentId\":\"e081b6be\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T14:35:32.554Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_b9ecab84ba464a6ba1ea7203\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"#!/usr/bin/env tsx\\n\\n/**\\n * 生成当日碎片信息汇总报告\\n * 每晚10:01执行\\n */\\n\\nimport fs from 'fs';\\nimport path from 'path';\\n\\nconst FRAGMENTS_DIR = '/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/fragments';\\nconst REPORTS_DIR = '/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/reports/daily';\\n\\n// 获取当前日期（北京时间）\\nfunction getTodayDate(): string {\\n  const now = new Date();\\n  const year = now.getFullYear();\\n  const month = String(now.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0');\\n  const day = String(now.getDate()).padStart(2, '0');\\n  return `${year}-${month}-${day}`;\\n}\\n\\n// 获取当前时间戳\\nfunction getTimestamp(): string {\\n  const now = new Date();\\n  const hours = String(now.getHours()).padStart(2, '0');\\n  const minutes = String(now.getMinutes()).padStart(2, '0');\\n  return `${hours}:${minutes}`;\\n}\\n\\n// 读取当日碎片信息\\nfunction readDailyFragments(date: string): string {\\n  const filePath = path.join(FRAGMENTS_DIR, `${date}.md`);\\n\\n  if (!fs.existsSync(filePath)) {\\n    return null;\\n  }\\n\\n  return fs.readFileSync(filePath, 'utf-8');\\n}\\n\\n// 生成日报\\nfunction generateDailyReport(date: string): string {\\n  const fragments = readDailyFragments(date);\\n\\n  if (!fragments) {\\n    return `# 📅 每日碎片信息汇总\\\\n\\\\n## ${date}\\\\n\\\\n今日暂无碎片信息记录。`;\\n  }\\n\\n  // 统计条目数\\n  const entries = fragments.split('\\\\n## ').filter(e => e.trim()).length;\\n\\n  return `# 📅 每日碎片信息汇总\\n\\n## ${date} - ${getTimestamp()}\\n\\n**共收集 ${entries} 条碎片信息**\\n\\n---\\n\\n${fragments}\\n`;\\n}\\n\\n// 保存日报\\nfunction saveDailyReport(date: string, report: string): void {\\n  const filePath = path.join(REPORTS_DIR, `${date}.md`);\\n\\n  if (!fs.existsSync(REPORTS_DIR)) {\\n    fs.mkdirSync(REPORTS_DIR, { recursive: true });\\n  }\\n\\n  fs.writeFileSync(filePath, report, 'utf-8');\\n}\\n\\n// 主函数\\nfunction main(): void {\\n  const date = getTodayDate();\\n  const report = generateDailyReport(date);\\n  saveDailyReport(date, report);\\n\\n  console.log(report);\\n}\\n\\nmain();\\n\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1772807732551}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"17b06e37\",\"parentId\":\"80775600\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T14:35:37.350Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"I see the issue. The daily-report.ts script only generates and saves the report, but it doesn't have any functionality to send it to 弗尼. The HEARTBEAT.md says \\\"发送: 汇总结果通过消息发送给弗尼\\\" but the script doesn't implement this.\\n\\nI need to modify the script to send the report to 弗尼 using the message tool. Let me first check what 弗尼's user ID is, and then I'll need to enhance the script to send the report.\\n\\nFrom the earlier conversation metadata, I can see that 弗尼's ID is \\\"ou_8887dbdc7941e5e195689f13804a3485\\\".\\n\\nI should update the script to send the report to 弗尼 via Feishu. Let me modify the daily-report.ts to include this functionality.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_a0a42da08e464975b60a6d09\",\"name\":\"edit\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/skills/fragment-organizer/daily-report.ts\",\"newText\":\"#!/usr/bin/env tsx\\n\\n/**\\n * 生成当日碎片信息汇总报告\\n * 每晚10:01执行\\n */\\n\\nimport fs from 'fs';\\nimport path from 'path';\\nimport { execSync } from 'child_process';\\n\\nconst FRAGMENTS_DIR = '/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/fragments';\\nconst REPORTS_DIR = '/workspace/projects/workspace-pm/reports/daily';\\nconst 弗尼_ID = 'ou_8887dbdc7941e5e195689f13804a3485';\",\"oldText\":\"#!/usr/bin/env tsx\\n\\n/**\\n * 生成当日碎片信息汇总报告\\n * 每晚10:01执行\\n */\\n\\nimport fs from 'fs';\\nimport path from 'path';\\n\\nconst FRAGMENTS_DIR = '/workspace/projects/workspace